						<summary>

						<p>Fragment of a slab lying in front of the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary and damaged. It seems to register a gift of land to Lingābattuḍu of Rāyala Cheruvu for some construction in the Chennakēśava temple at Bīmagoṇḍam. In characters of 16th century A.D.</p>						

